com.github.yona168.giraffe.net.messenger.client

Interface Client

  • All Superinterfaces:
    CanProcessPackets, Toggled
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    GClient

    public Client
extends Toggled, CanProcessPackets

    Defines the basic functionality of a client. Giraffe implements this with class GClient.

      • getSessionUUID

        java.util.UUID getSessionUUID()

        The UUID given to the client by some server that it connects to. This allows for clients to easily target other clients by referencing their session UUID in a interface SendablePacket. This is null if the server has not told the client its UUID
